10-judges-trailer/03/2018/|title=Shania Twain, \"Broad City\" Stars And More Join The Judges' Panel On \"Drag Race\" Season 10|publisher=}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Bob's Burgers]]'' || Hayden (voice) || Episode: \"Just One of the Boyz 4 Now for Now\"\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[The Romanoffs]]'' || David Patton || Episode: \"Bright and High Circle\"\n|-\n| 2018 || ''[[Live from Lincoln Center|Live from Lincoln Center: Stars in Concert]]''|| || Episode \"Andrew Rannells in Concert\" (Season 1)<ref>{{Cite episode |title=Andrew Rannells in Concert |episode-link= |url=https://www.pbs.org/live-from-lincoln-center/home/ |access-date=2020-03-21 |series=Live from Lincoln Center: Stars in Concert |series-link= |first= |last= |network=PBS |station= |date=2018 |season=1 |series-no= |number= |minutes= |time= |transcript= |transcript-url= |quote= |language=}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Black Monday (TV series)|Black Monday]]'' || Blair Pfaff ||\n|-\n| 2020 || ''[[Invincible (TV series)|Invincible]]'' || William Cockwell (voice) || 8 episodes\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year !! Title !! Voice role !! Notes\n|-\n| 2004 || ''Yu-Gi-Oh! Capsule Monster Coliseum'' || Mako Tsunami || English dub\n|-\n| 2005 || ''[[Shadow the Hedgehog (video game)|Shadow the Hedgehog]]''<ref>{{cite web |title=Andrew Rannells |url=https://www.behindthevoiceactors.com/Andrew-Rannells/ |website=Behind the Voice Actors |publisher=Behind the Voice Actors |accessdate=16 September 2018}}</ref> || Additional characters || English dub\n|-\n| 2006 || ''[[Bully (video game)|Bully]]'' || Bif Taylor ||\n|-\n| 2006 || ''[[One Piece: Pirates Carnival]]'' || Bellamy the Hyena || English dub\n|}\n\n===Theatre===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2000\u201301 || ''[[Pok\u00e9mon Live!]]'' || James || Baritone/Tenor\n|-\n| 2005 || ''[[Hairspray (musical)|Hairspray]]'' || Fender, [[Link Larkin]] || Replacement roles<ref>{{cite web|url=htt